steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit015l" and Comment "[INDEX-ENUM]"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit015l" display
When I add new column with Name "indexenum" Type "enum_type" for Table name "jit015l"
When I open popup to see column infos Name "indexenum" of table with Name "jit015l"
When I check checkbox popup Name "Indexed"
When I press Save button modal popup
Then I should see dropdown Index column index "1" of Index number "1" of table "jit015l" has value "indexenum" in retry mode
